<div class="prose">

<p>A peer audience that asks tough but fair questions. Engaged and curious — skeptical the way a good audience is, not hostile. Used in <strong>U3</strong> defense rehearsal (peer city councillor), <strong>U4</strong> policy panel, <strong>U5</strong> stakeholder roundtable, <strong>U6</strong> regional planning board, <strong>U7</strong> skeptical public reader. Tell it which unit you're rehearsing for and it sets the role.</p>

